dialogueTree.title: Elizabeth: ""*This* is what I studied law for?""
dialogueTree.english: "*This* is what I studied law for?"

dialogueTree.title: Elizabeth: ""Titus, you were told to keep a low..."
dialogueTree.english: "Titus, you were told to keep a low profile."

dialogueTree.title: Elizabeth: ""Can't wait to change out of these..."
dialogueTree.english: "Can't wait to change out of these rags."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie mogę się doczekać, żeby zrzucić te łachy”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: „Не магу дачакацца, каб скінуць гэтыя анучы”.

dialogueTree.title: Elizabeth: ""Evrart isn't paying me enough for..."
dialogueTree.english: "Evrart isn't paying me enough for this."
dialogueTree.polish: „Evrart za mało mi za to płaci”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Эўрар занадта мала мне за гэта плаціць».
